  "texts": [
    "We used the model with 7 billion parameters with chatting capability (7B-Chat version).",
    "This model has a limit of context length of maximum 4096 tokens.",
    "We used high performance computing system with the parameters specified in Additional file 1: Table S2.We have queried Llama-2 for 100 randomly selected GDAs out of 281 mismatched GDAs.",
    "Because of limited context size (4096 tokens) and to reduce the burden on Llama-2 of contextualizing the full entry page, we prompted Llama-2 with only the text from \"Molecular Genetics\" section.",
    "Additional file 1: Fig."
  ]
